Product Description

UGREEN Mini Displayport to HDMI Adapter

The UGREEN Mini DisplayPort to HDMI adapter can seamlessly connect a Mini DisplayPort/Thunderbolt port compatible PC or graphic card (like MacBook Pro, MacBook Air, iMac, Mac mini, Mac Pro, Lenovo ThinkPad and Microsoft Surface Pro ) to an HDTV, monitor, or projector with HDMI cable

Support Audio & Video over One Cable

***Supports video resolutions up to 1920 x 1200 and 1080p (Full HD)

***Supports uncompressed audio such as LPCM

***Supports compressed audio such as DTS Digital, Dolby Digital (including DTS-HD & Dolby True HD)

***HDCP Compliant

Wide Compatibility

2015 Apple MacBook, MacBook Pro, MacBook Air, iMac, Mac mini, Mac Pro

Microsoft Surface Pro/Pro 2/Pro 3 for Windows 8 Pro (NOT Surface/Surface 2 for Windows RT)

Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon, X230/240s, L430/440, L530/540, T430/440, T440s, T440p, T530/540p, W530/540, Helix

Dell XPS 13/14/15/17, Latitude E7240/E7440, Precision M3800, Alienware 14/17/18

Acer Aspire, Intel NUC, Asus Zenbook UX303LA/UX303LN

HP Envy 14/17, Google Chromebook Pixel

Cyberpower Zeusbook Edge X6-100/X6-200

Toshiba Satellite Pro S500, Tecra M11/A11/S11

**Kindly Note**

This adapter only works with PCs or graphic cards with Mini Displayport(thunderbolt 2.0), please check with your device's output specification prior to placing your order.
